Power Monitoring library : pm_lib

This software is a simple API that end users can use to
read the Cray XC Power Monitoring counters.

IT IS NOT OFFICIAL CRAY SOFTWARE AND IS ONLY TO BE USED
WITHIN OR DISTRIBUTED BY THE EU CRESTA RESEARCH PROJECT
UNDER THE CONDITIONS NOTED NEXT.

This software is distributed under the license provided
in the LICENSE file elsewhere in the distribution.

See the USAGE file for information on using the API
Note that you can test using the sys/ files here if
you change the definition for syspmcdir in pm_lib.c 
although returned values will of course not change.

-- Harvey Richardson, Cray UK Ltd, September 2014
